quran[50]{c,v,t}:
  15,50,Uye kuti zvirokwazvo marwadzo angu marwadzo akaomarara
  15,51,Uye vaudze nezve vaenzi (ngirozi) vaAbrahamu
  15,52,"Pavakapinda maakanga ari, vakati: “Salaam (Rugare)!” (Abrahamu) akati: “Zvirokwazvo! Tirikukutyai.”"
  15,53,"(Ngirozi) dzikati: “Usatye! Zvirokwazvo, tiri kukupa mashoko akanaka emwanakomana ane ruzivo nehungwaru.”"
  15,54,"(Abrahamu) akati: “Muri kundipa mashoko akanaka (emwanakomana) ini ndachembera? Saka nhau yenyu ndeyeyi?”"
  15,55,"(Ngirozi) dzikati: “Tinokupa mashoko akanaka muchokwadi. Saka usave weavo vasina tarisiro.”"
  15,56,"(Abrahamu) akati: “Ndiani asina tarisiro yenyasha dzaTenzi vake kusara kweavo vakarasika?”"
  15,57,"(Abrahamu) akatizve: “Saka nyaya yenyu ndeipi, imi vatumwa?”"
  15,58,"(Ngirozi) dzikati: “Zvirokwazvo, tave tinotumwa kune vanhu vasingatendi (vanotadza).”"
  15,59,“Kusara kwemhuri yaLut (Loti). Zvirokwazvo tichave tinovadzivirira (tinovanunura) vese (kubva mukuparadzwa).”
  15,60,"“Kusara kwemukadzi wake, uyo takava tinotara zvirokwazvo kuti achave weavo vanosara mumashure (vanoparadzwa).”"
  15,61,Naizvozvo vatumwa (ngirozi) pavakauya kune mhuri yaLut (Loti)
  15,62,"(Loti) Akati: “Zvirokwazvo, muri vanhu vasingazivikanwi kwandiri.”"
  15,63,"(Ngirozi) Dzikati: “Asi tauya kwauri neizvo zvavaisatenda mazviri.”"
  15,64,"“Uye taunza chokwadi kwauri (nyaya yekuparadzwa kwevanhu vako), uye zvirokwazvo, tinotaura chokwadi.”"
  15,65,"“Saka chiva unofamba muchidimbu cheusiku nemhuri yako, uye iwe wotevera kumashure kwavo, uye pakati penyu ngapasave nemunhu anocheuka kumashure, asi endai kwamakakomekedzwa.”"
  15,66,"Uye takaita basa iri kuti rizivikamwe kwaari, kuti midzi yeavo (vatadzi) ichave inodamburwa mangwanani ngwanani"
  15,67,Uye vagari vemudhorobha vakauya vachifara (nenyaya yemajaya ange auya aya)
  15,68,"(Loti) Akati: “Zvirokwazvo, ava vaenzi vangu, saka musandinyadzisewo.”"
  15,69,“Uye ityai Allah uye musave munondinyadzisa.”
  15,70,"(Vagari vemudhorobha) vakati: “Hatina kukurambidza here kutambira (kana kudzivirira) vanhu?”"
  15,71,"(Loti) akati: “Ava vanasikana vangu (kana muchida kuroora zviri pamutemo), kana muchikwanisa kudaro.”"
  15,72,"Zvirokwazvo, ndinopika nehupenyu hwako (Muhammad (SAW)), zvirokwazvo varimukudhakwa vaingofamba"
  15,73,Naizvozvo vakava vanoparadzwa neAs-Swaaihah (Ruzha) panguva dzemangwanani
  15,74,"Uye takapindurudza (Sodom kuPalestine) tikaita kuti pamusoro paende pasi, uye tikave tinonaisa matombo akaumbwa nedhaka"
  15,75,"Zvirokwazvo, mukati meizvi mune micherechedzo kune avo vanoona"
  15,76,"Uye zvirokwazvo, maguta maviri aya akanga ari munzira hombe (kubva kuMakkah kuenda kuSyria, pane gungwa reDead Sea iyezvino)"
  15,77,"Zvokwadi, zvirokwazvo mune izvi mune mucherechedzo kune avo vanotenda"
  15,78,Uye vagari vemusango (vekuMadyan (Midian)) avo vakatumirwa Muporofita Shuaib (AS)) vakanga vari vanhu vaiita zvakaipa
  15,79,Naizvozvo takatsiva nemutongo wakaomarara kwavari. Ari maviri ari munzira hombe iri pachena
  15,80,"Uye zvirokwazvo, vagari vemu Al-Hijr (Nzvimbo ine matombo) vakaramba vatumwa"
  15,81,"Uye takavapa zviratidzo zvedu, asi vakazviramba"
  15,82,"Uye vaigadzira dzimba mumakomo, vachifunga kuti vakachengetedzeka"
  15,83,Asi vakave vanoparadzwa neruzha munguva dzemangwanani (pazuva rechina kubva kumazuva vange vavimbiswa murango)
  15,84,Uye zvavaiwana hazvina kukwanisa kuvabatsira
  15,85,"Hatina kusika matenga nenyika nezvese zviri pakati pazvo asi muzvokwadi, uye zvirokwazvo nguva ichakwana, saka naizvozvo iva (Muhammad (SAW)) unovaregerera mune zvakanaka. (Izvi zvange zvakadaro kurwa (munzira yaAllah) kusati kwakomekedzwa"
  15,86,"Zvirokwazvo, Tenzi vako ndivo musiki vanoziva zvese"
  15,87,"Uye zvirokwazvo, takupa Al-Mathaani (ndima nomwe dzinoramba dzichidzokorodzwa, Surah Al-Faatihah), pamwe neQur’aan hombe"
  15,88,"Usava zvirokwazvo unotarisa nemaziso ako aine ruchiva pane izvo zvatakapa mamwe mapoka avo (vasingatendi), uye usava unobatikana pamusoro pavo. Uye iva unodzikisa mapapiro ako kune avo vanotenda (kuvaremekedza)"
  15,89,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Zvirokwazvo, inini ndiri muyambiri ari pachena.”"
  15,90,"Sekudzikisa kwatakaita kune avo vanopatsanura (maQuraish anonamata zvidhori, kana maJudha nemaKristu)"
  15,91,Avo vakapatsanura Qur’aan muzvidimbu zvidumbu (vakatenda muzvimwe uye vakaramba zvimwe)
  15,92,"Saka ndinopika naTenzi vako (Muhammad (SAW)), zvirokwazvo, tichava tinovabvunza vese"
  15,93,Maererano neizvo zvavaiita
  15,94,"Naizvozvo paridza pachena zvawakakomekedzwa (Islaam), ova unosiyana neavo vasingatendi"
  15,95,Zvirokwazvo! Tichava tinokukwanira kune avo vanokushoropodza
  15,96,Avo vanosanganisa Allah neumwe mwari; asi vachasvika pakuziva
  15,97,"Zvirokwazvo, tinoziva kuti zvavanotaura zvinokubata-bata muhana mako"
  15,98,Naizvozvo rumbidza kurumbidzwa kwaTenzi vako uye ova pakati peavo vanopfugama
  15,99,Uye namata Tenzi vako kusvikira rufu rwauya kwauri